	(72,27,'Pufy','Beutler51@wp.com','http://web.pakiet.hsms.pl/11233,art,Worki-sako-pufy-siedziska.html','94.60.169.24','2011-04-28 23:45:26','2011-04-28 23:45:26','I would like to thank you for the efforts you have made in publishing this article. I am hoping the same best work from you in the future as well. In fact your fanciful writing abilities has urged me to start my own blog now. Actually the blogging is spreading its wings rapidly. Your write up is a fine example of it.',0,'spam','Mozilla/5.0 (Windows; U; Windows NT 5.1; de; rv:1.9.1.3) Gecko/20090824 Firefox/3.5.3 (.NET CLR 3.5.30729)','',0,0),
	(60,59,'Blackberry 8520 Review','Magouyrk421@gmail.com','http://reviewers.co.za/smart-phones/blackberry-8520-review.htm','173.234.181.105','2011-04-22 14:50:01','2011-04-22 14:50:01','My husband and i were quite relieved  Peter managed to round up his survey through your precious recommendations he obtained while using the web pages. It\'s not at all simplistic to just continually be making a gift of helpful hints  the rest have been selling. And we all recognize we need the website owner to give thanks to because of that. The most important explanations you have made, the simple blog navigation, the relationships your site assist to promote - it\'s got many overwhelming, and it\'s making our son in addition to our family do think the idea is satisfying, and that is rather essential. Many thanks for the whole thing!',0,'spam','Mozilla/4.0 (compatible; MSIE 7.0; Windows NT 5.1; .NET CLR 1.1.4322; .NET CLR 2.0.50727; .NET CLR 3.0.04506.30)','',0,0),
	(61,56,'Cathy','Lunan434@aol.com','http://alphafolk.000a.biz/blog/imwalking/','178.19.126.224','2011-04-23 15:18:59','2011-04-23 15:18:59','I honestly knew about most of this, but with that in mind, I still thought it turned out valuable. Great work!',0,'spam','Mozilla/5.0 (Windows; U; Windows NT 5.1; en-US; rv:1.9.0.14) Gecko/2009082707 Firefox/3.0.14 (.NET CLR 3.5.30729)','',0,0),
	(62,47,'penis enlargement','mattcut90@gmail.com','http://www.buypenisenlargement.com','178.32.81.224','2011-04-23 23:53:05','2011-04-23 23:53:05','I would like to thank you for the efforts youve got produced in writing this article. I am hoping the same finest operate from you inside the potential also. Actually your creative writing skills has inspired me to start my personal BlogEngine weblog now.',0,'spam','Mozilla/4.0 (compatible; MSIE 6.0; Windows NT 5.0; KTXN)','',0,0),
	(69,27,'projekty domow','Byod@ymail.com','http://www.skupaut.pisser.pl/projekty-domow-przeciez-nie-tylko-beton/','87.237.62.174','2011-04-26 23:28:32','2011-04-26 23:28:32','Sorry for the huge review, but I\'m really loving the new Zune, and hope this, as well as the excellent reviews some other people have written, will help you decide if it\'s the right choice for you.',0,'spam','Mozilla/5.0 (Windows; U; Windows NT 5.1; pl; rv:1.9.1.3) Gecko/20090824 Firefox/3.5.3','',0,0),
	(68,27,'vimax','Mcnelley@gmail.com','http://vimax3-4.com','110.137.49.172','2011-04-26 13:47:16','2011-04-26 13:47:16','Just discovered this blog thru Bing, what a pleasant surprise! Regards: SB2011LAIN_AING',0,'spam','Mozilla/4.0 (compatible; MSIE 6.0; Windows NT 5.1; en) Opera 8.50','',0,0),
	(57,47,'Johnny Damms','Spycher5733@aim.com','http://yesprep.org/member/18749','184.82.83.85','2011-04-14 22:11:36','2011-04-14 22:11:36','Normally I do not read article on blogs, however I wish to say that this write-up very forced me to check out and do so! Your writing taste has been surprised me. Thank you, quite nice post.',0,'spam','Mozilla/4.0 (compatible; MSIE 6.0; Windows NT 5.1; en) Opera 8.50','',0,0),
