	(67,27,'vimax','Lomuscio@gmail.com','http://vimax3-4.com','200.175.3.247','2011-04-26 13:14:17','2011-04-26 13:14:17','I think this should be 1, as this sketch is a bit older than the one I posted last week. The willow tree shows a definite influence from SB2011LAIN_AING',0,'spam','Opera/9.64(Windows NT 5.1; U; en) Presto/2.1.1','',0,0),
	(63,1,'to lose weight','to.lose.weight35@yahoo.com','http://how-do-i-lose-weight-fast.info','68.185.71.93','2011-04-24 02:52:25','2011-04-24 02:52:25','I really liked your blog! It helped me alot...',0,'spam','Mozilla/5.0 (Windows; U; Windows NT 5.1; pt-BR; rv:1.8.1.13) Gecko/20080311 Firefox/2.0.0.13','',0,0),
	(64,27,'penis enlargement','mattcut90@gmail.com','http://www.buypenisenlargement.com','178.32.81.224','2011-04-24 14:22:23','2011-04-24 14:22:23','Another copy and paste blog post? Yours,',0,'spam','Mozilla/4.0 (compatible; MSIE 6.0; Windows NT 5.1; SV1)','',0,0),
	(65,49,'Linda','lindababyy@hotmail.com','','216.24.200.218','2011-04-25 17:00:47','2011-04-25 17:00:47','Image Exif data is useful to for image forensics. But EXIF data won\'t tell you too much - the user might have loaded the photo into something like Photoshop just to crop it the way he wanted. Site <a href=\"http://www.pskiller.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Photoshopped Image Killer</a> is beyond that, it mines structural information from image content and classifies image as original or altered based on that.',0,'spam','','',0,0),
	(66,27,'Thumbprint Cookies','Parjkffco5@gmail.com','http://www.thumbprint-cookies.com/','119.137.78.27','2011-04-25 20:38:29','2011-04-25 20:38:29','Ohh very much thanks admin.',0,'spam','Mozilla/5.0 (Windows; U; Windows NT 5.1; en-US; rv:1.9.0.14) Gecko/2009082707 Firefox/3.0.14 (.NET CLR 3.5.30729)','',0,0),
	(70,49,'StevenB','pergelater@gmail.com','','96.44.153.175','2011-04-27 03:49:34','2011-04-27 03:49:34','Fantastic image forensics tool: <a href=\"http://www.pskiller.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">pskiller.com</a>. Have you ever wondered if an image was altered with Photoshop? This website can give you the answer through content-level image analysis.',0,'spam','','',0,0),
	(71,27,'projekty domow','Pile@yahoo.com','http://www.skupaut.pisser.pl/projekty-domow-przeciez-nie-tylko-beton/','118.96.217.175','2011-04-27 11:27:09','2011-04-27 11:27:09','Zune and iPod: Most people compare the Zune to the Touch, but after seeing how slim and surprisingly small and light it is, I consider it to be a rather unique hybrid that combines qualities of both the Touch and the Nano. It\'s very colorful and lovely OLED screen is slightly smaller than the touch screen, but the player itself feels quite a bit smaller and lighter. It weighs about 2/3 as much, and is noticeably smaller in width and height, while being just a hair thicker.',0,'spam','Mozilla/5.0 (Windows; U; Windows NT 6.1; en-GB; rv:1.9.1.3) Gecko/20090824 Firefox/3.5.3','',0,0),
	(73,27,'Pufa','Foos9@wp.com','http://www.strony24.malbork.pl/a/Pufy-fotele-sako-worki-sako,3845','94.60.169.24','2011-04-29 10:59:17','2011-04-29 10:59:17','Your blog would increase in ranking if you post more often.',0,'spam','Opera/9.64(Windows NT 5.1; U; en) Presto/2.1.1','',0,0);
